item.title: [+483] The 7 Best and the 7 Worst TV Spinoffs of All Time
item.description: TV spin-offs are an easy way for studios to capitalize on a viewer's addictions to the most successful shows on television. But sadly, they usually end in a travesty, like when we were left watching "Billy" (1992), the lame spin-off of "Head of the Class" (1986). However, some spin-offs are great, and in a few cases, They're even better!
